  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12"  style="border-right: 1px solid black; border-left: 1px solid black; border-bottom: 1px solid black;">
    <p class="linejump">
    <b>In Short:</b> Yes, if you are a resident of California, you are granted specific rights regarding access to your personal information.
    </p>
    <p class="linejump">
